name: ufal.udpipe
documentation_summary: The HTML text outlines the structure and content of a webpage for the Institute of Formal and Applied Linguistics at Charles University, Czech Republic. It includes theme debug calls and file name suggestions for various templates (html, region, page, block, node) used in the site's Drupal theme. The page features information about the UDPipe tool, available in two versions with details on their performance and usage. UDPipe 1 is noted for its speed and UDPipe 2 for its excellent morphosyntactic performance. A new version, UDPipe 3, is also mentioned. Additionally, the page includes general information about the institute, such as events, research projects, grants, data tools, publications, industry cooperation, and contact details.
